&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Mission: Why Lighthouse?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At Lighthouse, we’re on a mission to revolutionize commercial strategy as hospitality’s most powerful AI platform. We take the world&#39;s largest hotel data network and transform it into real-time intelligence that drives action. We don&#39;t just deliver insights; we empower businesses to make decisions that move revenue.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
